message:
Origami Design Prototyping 
Origami is a free tool for designing modern user interfaces. Quickly put together a prototype, run it on your iPhone or iPad, iterate on it, and export code snippets your engineers can use. 

Origami created to design and build many of products Facebook, including Instagram, Paper, Messenger, Slingshot, Rooms, and Groups. 

http://facebook.github.io/origami/
http://facebook.github.io/origami/examples/
